Plot: From the #1 New York Times-bestselling master of paranormal romance comes the latest installment in the Meredith Gentry series. As tension continues to mount, Merry refuses the throne of faerie and seeks to create a haven for her unborn children.
Characters: Doyle, Rhys, Meredith "Merry" Gentry, Sean Galen, Frost (Killing Frost), Mistral, Barinthus, Royal, Bittersweet, Sholto, Kitto
